message.content:
cs.NI, cs.RO, cs.CR, cs.SY, cs.IT

This paper deals with the use of drones for cellular network coverage in disaster-struck regions, which involves aspects of networking (cs.NI), robotics (cs.RO), control (cs.CR), system engineering (cs.SY), and information theory (cs.IT). However, since the focus is primarily on the networking aspect, cs.NI is the most likely sub-category, followed by cs.RO for the use of drones, and then cs.CR, cs.SY, and cs.IT for the optimization and control aspects.
